name: Kaseler Alm
description:
Info:

audience: beginners to professionals

number of boulders: 90

starting point: parking lot of the climbing area

access: Follow the road from Ginzling in the direction of Schlegeis. After the bridge, past a small water reservoir, you'll see the boulders on the righthand side in a field. 500 meters furtheron there is the new parking lot of the climbing area.

period: April - November (dependent on the weather)
